OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers across the region. Showers may
OL,7,Fbe heavy and merge into longer spells
OL,8,Fof rain at times. Pleasant in any
OL,9,Fsunshine, but otherwise feeling rather
OL,10,Fcool for June in a blustery breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers easing to leave a
OL,13,Fcool evening with late sunny spells.
OL,14,FTemperatures rebounding slightly as
OL,15,Fcloud builds overnight, with rain
OL,16,Farriving from the west during the
OL,17,Fearly hours of Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
