OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA wet morning as rain
OL,6,Fspreads across the region, locally
OL,7,Fheavy at times. Rain turning lighter
OL,8,Fand patchier in the afternoon, but
OL,9,Fremaining widely cloudy. Feeling muggy
OL,10,Fdespite being windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,13,Fcloudy and breezy on Friday with
OL,14,Fpatchy rain. Drier and warmer over the
OL,15,Fweekend, with winds also easing. Sunny
OL,16,Fspells emerging, but low cloud and fog
OL,17,Flingering along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
